Package com.ae2dms.GameMap

Class Level

java.lang.Object
com.ae2dms.GameMap.Level
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<GameObject>
public final class Level
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<GameObject>

The Class Level defines the level object in the game. Every level in the game is an object. Defines some level fields and method that manipulate the level object.
